advancing
$MUDNAME$ Concepts Help
advancing

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
On $MUDNAME$ you advance by increasing individual skills.  Skills are modelled as a tree.  At first you'll only see the top-level of this tree, but as you advance the tree will expand.

There are two ways to advance on $MUDNAME$:
.EP

.SH Taskmaster
.SP 5 5
The taskmaster is a system that awards skill increases as you use your skills.  Taskmaster awards are shown in yellow on colour terminals.
.EI
.SP 5 5
.SH Advancing
.SP 5 5
You can advance at the academy for a small fee.  Which skills can be advanced, and how much it costs depends on your stats.
.EI
.SP 5 5

.SH See Also:
.SI 5
skills, taskmaster, advance
.EI
